title: LXXXV: Liv is Finally Obsessed with Lore Olympus, a 3 Year Anniversary Q&A
itunes:title: LXXXV: Liv is Finally Obsessed with Lore Olympus, a 3 Year Anniversary Q&A
itunes:subtitle: Lore Olympus (finally!), Cupid and Psyche, and just about everything else!
description:
It's that time again! Your questions, my answers. I talk Lore Olympus (finally!), Cupid and Psyche, Hellenism, the gods and goddesses, and just about everything else!


CW/TW: far too many Greek myths involve assault. Given it's fiction, and typically involves gods and/or monsters, I'm not as deferential as I would be were I referencing the real thing.


Attributions and licensing information for music used in the podcast can be found here: mythsbaby.com/sources-attributions.
